 (the Andromeda and the Milky\nWay galaxies), and of the order of the mass required to dynamically stabilize\nthe Local Group.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 31 Jul 2002 22:06:16 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 4 Dec 2002 20:42:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2007-05-23"}
